  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个IaC采用旅程图，帮助领导层理解从0到1的完整路径。我设想分成四个阶段：Discovery、Pilot、Scale，最后还有一个持续优化阶段。你觉得这个框架合理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery",
        "Pilot",
        "Scale",
        "Optimisation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "框架很清晰。我想确认一下最后一个阶段的名字——您说的是\"持续优化\"，我注意到代码里常用\"Optimisation\"，用这个词可以吗？另外，每个阶段大概放几个关键活动？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Optimisation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就用\"Optimisation\"。每个阶段放两个核心活动吧。Discovery阶段先让架构团队\"Define adoption vision\"，然后平台小队评估\"Assess platform readiness\"，这两个都是打基础的工作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery",
        "Define adoption vision",
        "Architecture Team",
        "Assess platform readiness",
        "Platform Squad"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Discovery部分我先画上了。Pilot阶段我理解是落地第一个可用模块，\"Establish landing zone\"和\"Deliver first reusable module\"这两个活动对吗？评分方面平台小队建landing zone给4分，但交付模块需要产品团队配合，给5分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pilot",
        "Establish landing zone",
        "Deliver first reusable module",
        "Platform Squad",
        "Product Team"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Pilot阶段就是平台小队和产品的第一次深度协作。Scale阶段要放大招了：\"Automate guardrails\"和\"Onboard product teams\"，前者平台小队自己做，后者需要批量对接各产品团队。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scale",
        "Automate guardrails",
        "Onboard product teams",
        "Product Teams"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我发现之前\"Onboard product teams\"的参与方我写成了单数\"Product Team\"，但这里应该是多个产品团队吧？需要改成复数\"Product Teams\"。另外评分方面，批量上船比建landing zone难，但比第一个模块简单，给3分合适吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Onboard product teams",
        "Product Teams"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "改得对，是多个产品团队。评分3分合理，因为批量上船有标准流程了，反而比摸索期轻松。最后Optimisation阶段：\"Measure outcomes\"由架构和PMO一起评估，\"Continuous improvement loop\"需要平台小队和运维团队共建，这个闭环特别重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Optimisation",
